    "is_free": false,
    "description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3201450/extras/9bc3e3278f252209128a8f309deb3a8c.poster.avif?t=1750587952\" width=600 height=338 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3201450/extras/9bc3e3278f252209128a8f309deb3a8c.webm?t=1750587952\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3201450/extras/9bc3e3278f252209128a8f309deb3a8c.mp4?t=1750587952\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>暗黑堕落幸存者</strong>是一款Roguelite幸存者类游戏，每一局的技能和装备掉落都不同，为每次冒险带来独特的挑战。游戏拥有暗黑类游戏中经典的锻造、商店、成就和圣器等深度系统，玩家可以打造强大的装备和技能流派，体验无尽的战斗和策略组合的乐趣。</p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >守护最后的栖息之地</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>艾兰族</strong>，星光眷顾的高等精灵，在诸神的庇佑下封闭了精灵圣地，远离凡俗，安然繁衍已于万载。然而，暗黑堕落之力在大地深处悄然滋长，最终在万年后的今天侵蚀了大陆上的强者，将他们腐化为暗黑堕落者，并吞噬了艾兰族的辉煌。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >如今，族群凋零，文明衰颓，而你——最后的幸存者，背靠残存圣地，依托先祖神灵赐予的力量，抗衡无尽的暗黑兽潮，锻造圣器，迎战暗黑堕落之主，誓要让光明再度照耀圣地。</p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >高等精灵赐予祝福</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >六大高等精灵全程守护，每位精灵都会赋予你独特的能力，帮助你在暗黑世界中打造独特的战斗风格。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3201450/extras/f8eb8e0df0736b0afef90e447ad9ca1a.poster.avif?t=1750587952\" width=600 height=176 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3201450/extras/f8eb8e0df0736b0afef90e447ad9ca1a.webm?t=1750587952\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3201450/extras/f8eb8e0df0736b0afef90e447ad9ca1a.mp4?t=1750587952\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >多种英雄选择</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >多种英雄可供选择，提供不同的成长体系，解锁时装，拥有属于自己的独特魅力。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3201450/extras/1998f3187a384b0fd267f39825a0fbee.poster.avif?t=1750587952\" width=600 height=338 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3201450/extras/1998f3187a384b0fd267f39825a0fbee.webm?t=1750587952\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3201450/extras/1998f3187a384b0fd267f39825a0fbee.mp4?t=1750587952\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >打败暗黑堕落者，获得他们的圣器</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >刷宝掉落、商店和锻造系统，让玩家在不断地挑战中强化自己，打造属于自己的最强圣器</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3201450/extras/3ced3a4adcc2fa542f13fd66d7b1d411.poster.avif?t=1750587952\" width=600 height=338 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3201450/extras/3ced3a4adcc2fa542f13fd66d7b1d411.webm?t=1750587952\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3201450/extras/3ced3a4adcc2fa542f13fd66d7b1d411.mp4?t=1750587952\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >构建最强技能流派，挑战暗黑堕落者</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >每局身处不同危机，四十个强大恩赐，让你的战力迅速提升，构筑您最强的技能流派，挑战强大的暗黑堕落者，守护最后的圣地；</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3201450/extras/c1dbc23aa237d0c4a48d2b6d9762e69e.poster.avif?t=1750587952\" width=600 height=338 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3201450/extras/c1dbc23aa237d0c4a48d2b6d9762e69e.webm?t=1750587952\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3201450/extras/c1dbc23aa237d0c4a48d2b6d9762e69e.mp4?t=1750587952\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >更多内容待您解锁，敬请期待！！！</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p>",
